This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) because it deals with natural language processing and topic modeling. It could also belong to cs.IR (Information Retrieval) because topic modeling is often used in information retrieval tasks. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.LG (Machine Learning) because topic modeling is a machine learning technique. It could also be classified under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) because topic modeling is a subfield of AI. Finally, it could be categorized under cs.DL (Deep Learning) because the paper mentions Topical Word Embedding (TWE), which is a deep learning-based topic modeling technique.
